\c 6
\s Ngoro ina
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndakadzoka ndokusimudza meso angu, ndokuona, zvino tarira, ngoro ina dzinobuda kubva pakati pemakomo maviri, uye makomo makomo endarira.
\v 2 Pangoro yekutanga paiva nemabhiza matsvuku, uye pangoro yechipiri mabhiza matema,
\v 3 nepangoro yechitatu mabhiza machena, nepangoro yechina mabhiza mapfumbu ane simba.
\v 4 Zvino ndakapindura ndokuti kumutumwa waitaura neni: Izvi zvii, ishe wangu?
\v 5 Mutumwa ndokupindura ndokuti kwandiri: Iyi mweya mina yekumatenga inoburuka kubva pakumira pamberi paIshe wenyika yese.
\v 6 Mabhiza matema aripo anobuda kuenda kunyika yekumaodzanyemba; uye machena anobuda kuatevera, nemapfumbu anobuda achienda kunyika yekuchamhembe.
\v 7 Anesimba akabudawo, akatsvaka kufamba kuenda uko neuko panyika. Iye ndokuti: Fambai muende uko neuko panyika. Zvino akaenda uko neuko panenda kuti apote-pote nenyika yese; ikati: Ibvai pano, mupote-pote nenyika yese.
\v 8 Ipapo akadanidzira kwandiri, akataura neni, achiti: Tarira, vanoenda kunyika yokumaodzanyemba, vakanyaradza mweya wangu kunyika yokumaodzanyemba.
\s Korona pamusoro waJoshua
\p
\v 9 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri, richiti:
\v 10 Tora vamwe kunavakatapwa, vanoti Heridhai, naTobhiya, naJedhaia; uuye nezuva irero upinde mumba maJosiya mwanakomana waZefaniya, kwavakasvika vachibva Babhironi;
\v 11 utore kwavari sirivha negoridhe, uite korona, uidzike pamusoro waJoshua mwanakomana waJehozadhaki, mupristi mukukru;
\v 12 utaure naye, uchiti: Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo: Tarira, murume ane zita rinonzi Davi; iye achakura panzvimbo yake, iye achavaka tembere yaJehovha;
\v 13 ndiye achavaka tembere yaJehovha; iye achava noumambo, uye achagara pachigaro chake achibata ushe; achava mupristi pachigaro chake choushe; rangano yorugare ichava pakati pavo ivo vaviri.
\v 14 Korona dzichava dzaHeremi, naTobhiya, naJedhaia, naHeni mwanakomana waZefaniya, chive chiyeudzo mutembere yaJehovha.
\v 15 Vari kure vachauya vachivaka tembere yaJehovha; ipapo muchaziva kuti Jehovha wehondo ndiye akanditumira kwamuri. Izvezvi zvichaitika kana muchiteerera zvakanaka izwi raJehovha Mwari wenyu.
